@node "MAIN" "Noiseconverter Documentation"



                            @{b}Noiseconverter @{ub}

                             Version 1.53


                Copyright © 1993-1995 Defect Softworks
                        written by Henryk Richter

 
 Noiseconverter is a @{i}Freeware @{ui}Program to convert several Tracker related
 music formats into some other formats like Protracker`s module format,
 Quadracomposer`s EMODs or even the Art of Noise fileformat.



 @{" Distribution                     " link "Disclaimer" 0} redistribution conditions and copyright notes
 @{" Introduction                     " link "Introduction" 0} something about the reasons why I wrote it
