@node "Revision_History" "Revision History"

                        @{b}@{u}Revision History@{ub}@{uu}

    @{b}v1.53@{ub}       -added loader for @{"Polkarunner" link "Polkarunner" 0}
                -added saver for @{"Art of Noise" link "AONtext" 0}
                -numerous small changes, optimizations, bugfixes and
                 preparations for upcoming features
                -again a small @{"Ripper" link "The_Ripper_Window" 0} speed up
                -added support for @{"HCD Protector" link "HCDProt" 0}

    @{b}v1.52@{ub}       -added @{"Exotic ResetPatch" link "ExoticRipper" 0} / Chipsaver support
                -Ripper speed up (sometimes >50% faster)

    @{b}v1.51@{ub}       -added some formats:
                          @{"Amos Music Bank" link "Amos_Music_Bank" 0}
                          @{"Fuzzac Packer" link "Fuzzac_Packer" 0}
                          @{"Heatseeker MC1.0" link "Heatseeker_MC1.0" 0}
                          @{"TrackerPacker 1" link "Trackerpacker_1" 0}
                          @{"SoundtrackerPro 3.0" link "Soundtracker_PRO_3.0" 0} (with correct notes !)
                          @{"P61" link "The_Player_V5.0" 0} support
                -added a saver:
                          @{"Moduleprotector" link "Moduleprotector" 0}
                -when @{"altering Samplenames" link "rename_Sam" 0} the program switches now
                 automatically to the next samplename on "return" keystroke
                -fixed some problems with my temporary buffers, now they`re
                 cleared every time a module is loaded
                -little fixes in @{"SoundFX1.3" link "SoundFX_1.3" 0} loader

    @{b}v1.50@{ub}       first release with a documentation (sorry, I was too lazy)

    @{b}v1.02-v1.49@{ub} lots of versions over almost a year, don`t know what I
                changed all the time

    @{b}v1.01@{ub}       first public release
@endnode

